  "message": "chore(deps): bump proptest 1.10.0 -> 1.11.0 across dev-deps\n\nMinor bump of the `proptest` dev-dependency used in property-based\ntests across fnx-classes, fnx-convert, fnx-algorithms, fnx-generators,\nfnx-readwrite, fnx-conformance, and fnx-python.\n\nproptest 1.11.0 is a semver-compatible minor release over 1.10.0 with\nno breaking changes affecting existing `proptest!` / `Strategy` code.\n\nVerified with:\n  rch exec -- cargo update -p proptest\n  rch exec -- cargo check --workspace --all-targets\n  rch exec -- cargo test -p fnx-classes -p fnx-algorithms\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
